sequenceDiagram
    actor A as HRD / Admin
    participant FK as FormKinerja
    participant KC as KinerjaController
    participant DK as DataKinerja

    A->>FK: Input Nilai KPI & Klik Simpan()
    FK->>KC: SubmitNilaiKinerja()
    KC->>KC: KalkulasiTotalSkor()
    KC->>DK: SimpanPenilaian()
    DK-->>KC: Return: Data Tersimpan
    KC-->>FK: Tampilkan Alert Sukses()
